-- E3: 3-way guard chain hitting middle and last arms.
-- `otherwise` closes the chain; `__fallthrough__` is the unreachable sentinel.
-- label 5 = 1 (first arm: n > 0)
-- label 0 = 0 (middle arm: n == 0)
-- label (-3) = -1 (last arm: otherwise)
-- main = label 5 + label 0 * 10 + label (0 - 3) * 100
-- = 1 + 0 + (-1 * 100) = -99
label n
  | n > 0 = 1
  | n == 0 = 0
  | otherwise = -1

main = label 5 + label 0 * 10 + label (0 - 3) * 100
